Story: speccing a step

 As an Rspec User	
 I want to spec the steps to use in the stories	 
 So that they show a defined behavior

 Scenario: Step group doesn't exist - failing spec

  Given step 'Given a not implemented step'

  When I add before-expectation: true

  Then it should fail

 Scenario: Step not yet implemented - failing spec

  Given step 'Given a not implemented step'
  
  When I add before-expectation: true
  And I add step group :spec
 
  Then it should fail

 Scenario: trivial failing step

  Given step 'Given trivial failing step'

	When I add before-expectation: true
	And I add step group :spec

	Then it should fail

 Scenario: trivial passing step

  Given step 'Given trivial passing step'

	When I add before-expectation: true
	And I add step group :spec

	Then it should pass
  
  

 